Package bacnet.datamodel.proteomics

Class TIS

java.lang.Object
bacnet.datamodel.sequence.Sequence
bacnet.datamodel.proteomics.TIS
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class TIS extends Sequence implements Serializable
This class is used to regroup different Nterm. The assumption is that we regroup in a TIS every Nterm comes from the same peptide but are now different due to proteolysis and C-Terminal ragging
Author:
UIBC
